  "body": "As a user, i want to proceed with the screens that require confirmation (for example, OK button , Continue button) with ENTER key on keyboard the way when i hit ENTER on my keyboard -> I am being redirected to next available screen.\r\n\r\nWe have such a flow when backing up seed phrase:\r\n\r\n1. Open status\r\n2. Create new account\r\n3. Profile -> Privacy and Security\r\n4. Back up seed phrase\r\n5. Hit Enter when seeing CONTINUE button\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** next screen opens\r\n**Actual result:** can proceed only when clicking the button with a mouse\r\n\r\n**NOTE:** this could be a good thing to have it across the app (for example when creating an account and etc.)\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"483\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-04-22 в 12 14 03\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/115689590-e4771a80-a364-11eb-8f40-8db7b84da6d7.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"483\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-04-22 в 12 14 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/115689609-e8a33800-a364-11eb-85f6-caf528fa15fd.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Version:** `beta.8`\r\n**Node Version:** `StatusDesktop/v0.72.1/darwin-amd64/go1.13.4`\r\n**OS:** `MacOS Big Sur 11.2.3`",
